{"name":"Craft Spiritual Weapons","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Requirements </strong>Your familiar successfully @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.familiar-adventures-familiar-actions.adsfsHxuc7Gr3rGD]{Spiritual Harvested} during this encounter.</p>\n<p><strong>Skill </strong>Crafting;</p>\n<p><strong>DC </strong>a standard DC for your level, with a hard adjustment if this is a Severe or Extreme encounter</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Your familiar fashions together material into spiritual weaponry.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> Your familiar gains @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.familiar-adventures-effects.x88LoSzpE8A9z9vM]{2 Spirit Points}, and your familiar crafts a temporary duplicate of one of your weapons. It lasts until the end of the encounter. Your familiar can @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strike} with this weapon, using your spell attack modifier.</p>\n<p><strong>Success </strong>Your familiar gains @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.familiar-adventures-effects.x88LoSzpE8A9z9vM]{1 Spirit Point}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure </strong>No effect.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> Your familiar wastes spiritual resources and loses 1 Spirit Point.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"craft-spiritual-weapons","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["hb_familiar"]},"actionType":{"value":"action"},"category":"familiar","actions":{"value":1},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685767143535,"modifiedTime":1686134303577,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"CY6iT6uUkyBi7uAK"}
{"name":"Familiar Surge","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Requirements </strong>Your familiar has 4 Spirit Points.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Your familiar loses 4 Spirit Points. It casts any common cantrip from your tradition that requires 1 or 2 actions to cast, using your spell attack modifier and spell DC.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"familiar-surge","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["hb_familiar"]},"actionType":{"value":"action"},"category":"familiar","actions":{"value":1},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685767143535,"modifiedTime":1686134294574,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"IhWg9dg0awcweqrM"}
{"name":"Combat Spiritual Powers","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Skill </strong>Acrobatics, Athletics, or Stealth;</p>\n<p><strong>DC </strong>the target’s Will DC</p>\n<p><strong>Range </strong>60 feet;</p>\n<p><strong> Target </strong>1 creature </p>\n<hr />\n<p>Your familiar lashes out at the hidden powers that support your enemy.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Success </strong>Your familiar gains @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.familiar-adventures-effects.x88LoSzpE8A9z9vM]{2 Spirit Points} and decimates the hidden powers. The backlash of spiritual energy strikes at the target. Until the end of your next turn, successful @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.VjxZFuUXrCU94MWR]{Strikes} against the target deal an additional [[/r 1[mental]]] damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Success </strong>Your familiar gains @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.familiar-adventures-effects.x88LoSzpE8A9z9vM]{1 Spirit Point}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure </strong>No effect.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The spirits lash out at your familiar, dealing [[/r 1[mental]]] damage.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"combat-spiritual-powers","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["hb_familiar"]},"actionType":{"value":"action"},"category":"familiar","actions":{"value":1},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685767143535,"modifiedTime":1686134300173,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"PJPcFS0kDjpxLE3V"}
{"name":"Lend Spirit","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Requirements </strong>Your familiar has a Spirit Point</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Choose an ally’s familiar within 60 feet. Your familiar loses 1 Spirit Point and the chosen familiar gains @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.familiar-adventures-effects.x88LoSzpE8A9z9vM]{1 Spirit Point}.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"lend-spirit","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["hb_familiar"]},"actionType":{"value":"action"},"category":"familiar","actions":{"value":1},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685767143535,"modifiedTime":1686134306613,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"SPkfXzKorDutzlaQ"}
{"name":"Steal Soulshard","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Skill </strong>Thievery;</p>\n<p><strong>DC </strong>the target’s Will DC</p>\n<p><strong>Range </strong>60 feet;</p>\n<p><strong>Target </strong>1 creature </p>\n<hr />\n<p>Your familiar attempts to pilfer a piece of the target’s soul.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> Your familiar gains @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.familiar-adventures-effects.x88LoSzpE8A9z9vM]{2 Spirit Points}, and your familiar gains a +2 circumstance bonus on their next familiar action that targets the same creature.</p>\n<p><strong>Success </strong>Your familiar gains @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.familiar-adventures-effects.x88LoSzpE8A9z9vM]{1 Spirit Point}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure </strong>No effect.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature becomes immune to your familiar’s @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.familiar-adventures-familiar-actions.SeKK89YKnVxJOHBH]{Steal Soulshard}.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"steal-soulshard","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["hb_familiar"]},"actionType":{"value":"action"},"category":"familiar","actions":{"value":1},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685767143535,"modifiedTime":1686134289107,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"SeKK89YKnVxJOHBH"}
{"name":"Entreat Spirits","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Requirements </strong>Your familiar has a Spirit Point</p>\n<p><strong>Skill </strong>Deception, Diplomacy, or Performance;</p>\n<p><strong>DC </strong>the DC to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.1OagaWtBpVXExToo]{Recall Knowledge} about the target</p>\n<p><strong>Range </strong>60 feet;</p>\n<p><strong>Target </strong>1 creature </p>\n<hr />\n<p>Your familiar solicits information and favor from nearby spirits. The type of spirits depends on the creatures in the encounter: ghosts for undead; divine servitors for celestials, fiends, or monitors; alien minds for aberrations; etc.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> Your familiar gains @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.familiar-adventures-effects.x88LoSzpE8A9z9vM]{2 Spirit Points}, and the spirits reveal information to your familiar. You learn one piece of correct information about the target.</p>\n<p><strong>Success </strong>Your familiar gains @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.familiar-adventures-effects.x88LoSzpE8A9z9vM]{1 Spirit Point}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure </strong>No effect.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The spirits lash out at your familiar, dealing [[/r 1[mental]]] damage.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"entreat-spirits","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["hb_familiar"]},"actionType":{"value":"action"},"category":"familiar","actions":{"value":1},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685767143535,"modifiedTime":1686134305158,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"YmoQLNyNmuouUNUP"}
{"name":"Spiritual Harvest","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Skill </strong>Arcana, Nature, or Survival;</p>\n<p><strong>DC </strong>a standard DC for your level, with a hard adjustment if this is a Severe or Extreme encounter</p>\n<p><strong>Range </strong>60 feet </p>\n<hr />\n<p>Your familiar scrounges for spiritual resources in the area.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Success </strong>Your familiar gains @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.familiar-adventures-effects.x88LoSzpE8A9z9vM]{2 Spirit Points}, and your familiar imbues one weapon or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.FNDq4NFSN0g2HKWO]{Handwraps of Mighty Blows} with spiritual essence. Until the end of your next turn, this weapon deals [[/r 1[mental]]] damage on a miss (but not a critical miss) in addition to any other effects on a miss.</p>\n<p><strong>Success </strong>Your familiar gains @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.familiar-adventures-effects.x88LoSzpE8A9z9vM]{1 Spirit Point}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure </strong>No effect.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> Your familiar takes a -1 circumstance penalty on their next familiar action.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"spiritual-harvest","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["hb_familiar"]},"actionType":{"value":"action"},"category":"familiar","actions":{"value":1},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685767143535,"modifiedTime":1686134308232,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"adsfsHxuc7Gr3rGD"}
{"name":"Assess Spiritual Landscape","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Skill </strong>Arcana, Nature, Occultism, or Religion;</p>\n<p><strong>DC </strong>the highest DC to Recall Knowledge about any creature in the encounter </p>\n<hr />\n<p>Your familiar surveys the spiritual forces supporting your enemies.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> Your familiar gains@UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.familiar-adventures-effects.x88LoSzpE8A9z9vM]{2 Spirit Points} and gains keen insights into nearby spirits. Your familiar gains a +1 circumstance bonus on its next familiar action.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> Your familiar gains @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.familiar-adventures-effects.x88LoSzpE8A9z9vM]{1 Spirit Point}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure </strong>No effect.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The spirits confuse and confound your familiar. It takes a -1 circumstance penalty on its next familiar action.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"assess-spiritual-landscape","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["hb_familiar"]},"actionType":{"value":"action"},"category":"familiar","actions":{"value":1},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685767143535,"modifiedTime":1686134298452,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"dPA6KfTuhjXPf7GE"}
{"name":"Spiritual Roar","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Skills </strong>Intimidation or Performance;</p>\n<p><strong>DC </strong>the target’s Will DC</p>\n<p><strong>Range </strong>60 feet;</p>\n<p><strong>Target </strong>1 creature</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Your familiar makes a threatening display at the spiritual powers that support your enemies.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> Your familiar gains @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.familiar-adventures-effects.x88LoSzpE8A9z9vM]{2 Spirit Point} and sends the spiritual powers fleeing. If you give the target the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened} condition before the end of your next turn, they are also @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.AJh5ex99aV6VTggg]{Flat-Footed} against you while @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened}.</p>\n<p><strong>Success </strong>Your familiar gains @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.familiar-adventures-effects.x88LoSzpE8A9z9vM]{1 Spirit Point}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure </strong>No effect.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The spirits make a threatening display in return. Your familiar becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened 1}.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"spiritual-roar","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["hb_familiar"]},"actionType":{"value":"action"},"category":"familiar","actions":{"value":1},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685767143535,"modifiedTime":1686134310039,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"jyD3cLqmbBi0yzYO"}
{"name":"Craft Spiritual Armor","type":"action","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p><strong>Requirements </strong>Your familiar successfully @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.familiar-adventures-familiar-actions.adsfsHxuc7Gr3rGD]{Spiritual Harvested} during this encounter.</p>\n<p><strong>Skill </strong>Crafting;</p>\n<p><strong>DC </strong>a standard DC for your level, with a hard adjustment if this is a Severe or Extreme encounter</p>\n<p><strong>Range </strong>60 feet </p>\n<hr />\n<p>Your familiar fashions together material into spiritual protection.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> Your familiar gains @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.familiar-adventures-effects.x88LoSzpE8A9z9vM]{2 Spirit Points}, and your familiar crafts a temporary set of spiritual armor for you or an ally. The chosen creature gains resistance 1 against mental damage, or increases the resistance to mental damage by 1.</p>\n<p><strong>Success </strong>Your familiar gains @UUID[Compendium.frontiers-of-magic.familiar-adventures-effects.x88LoSzpE8A9z9vM]{1 Spirit Point}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure </strong>No effect.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> Your familiar wastes spiritual resources and loses 1 Spirit Point.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Frontiers of Magic"},"rules":[],"slug":"craft-spiritual-armor","schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["hb_familiar"]},"actionType":{"value":"action"},"category":"familiar","actions":{"value":1},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp","flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1685767143535,"modifiedTime":1686134301663,"lastModifiedBy":"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Gh9U9I93FE4tnAIO":3},"_id":"uIHbkRm0xzxoS6Fj"}
